## Troubleshooting
- **Project Not Found**: Ensure project exists in `.squads-ai/projects/`
- **Template Issues**: Check `templates/projects/` directory exists
- **Permission Errors**: Make script executable with `chmod +x scripts/plan-feature.sh`
- **Missing Files**: Verify all required project files exist

